    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase NHS Police Fire & Ambulance Staff personal allowance to \u00a335k for 12mths",
        "additional_details": "During this time of uncertainty we will be relying on our people on the front line of this battle with COVID 19. In recognition of this and to show our gratitude I feel our government should make a commitment to them, in order to make this a little easier. \r\nWe should be looking after the people who are looking after us.",
        "background": "I think we should increase the personal allowance of each NHS, Police, Fire and Ambulance staff to \u00a335k for the next 12 months, whilst we fight COVID 19.",
